DESCRIPTION: | Arena Wien - Gelände | DIY HARDCORE PUNK FEST  Here we go with the bands for the upcoming edition of DESTROY VIENNA!  18:00 doors 18:30 Zepter 19:20 Industry 20:05 Spiritual Law 20:50 Rifle 21:35 Brux 22:20 Nabat 23:15 Home Front  00:15 Klavo (Beisl) 00:45 Cosey Mueller (Beisl)  DAY 1:  G.B.H. – Hardcore Punk veterans from Birmingham ASPHALT - Hard hitting Garage Punk from Toulouse BRÅND – Black Metal Punk from Upper Austria VENENÖ - Dark and gloomy Post Punk from NYC LICKSPIT – Bandana Thrash from Cz THE DOGS - Pissed off Punk straight outta Welsh pubs BULL NAKANO - Uncrompromising groovy Harcore Punk from Vienna  DAY 2:  HOME FRONT – Post Punk maniacs from Edmonton KLAVO - Hard as nails Street Rock‘n‘Roll from Berlin BRUX - Dark and wavy Oi! from Barcelona NABAT - Oi! veterans from Bologna INDUSTRY - Berlin based peace punk quartet RIFLE - Punk with a Garage edge from London COSEY MUELLER – Cold Wave Synthpunk from Berlin ZEPTER – Killer Heavy Metal from Linz   Vorverkauf/Presale 2-Day-Pass Early Bird SOLD OUT Vorverkauf/Presale 2-Day-Pass Regular € 65 (inkl. Fees) Vorverkauf/Presale Day 1 € 38 (inkl. Fees) Vorverkauf/Presale Day 2 € 45 (inkl. Fees)
